== 评价 ==

《西格玛和声》在开始日本发售时排到了销售榜第八位，销量为23,000<ref>{{cite web | author=Jenkins, David | date=2008-08-28 | title=Japanese Charts: Soccer Releases Dominate In Slow Week | url=http://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=20017 | work=Gamasutra.com | accessdate=2009-04-14 | archive-date=2019-06-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615025952/https://gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=20017 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2008年9月30日，游戏在日本售出了70,000份。日本杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》为游戏打了31/40分<ref>{{cite web | author=Riley, Adam | date=2008-08-06 | title=Level-5's New Nintendo DS RPG Highly Rated by Famitsu | url=http://www.cubed3.com/news/10542/ | work=Cubed3.com | accessdate=2009-03-04 | archive-date=2012-05-04 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67Q0RwLyB?url=http://www.cubed3.com/news/10542/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

